---
import ReviewComponent from "../React/ReviewComponent";
---
<section class="py-20 text-white">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-8 md:px-12 lg:px-24">
    <div class="text-center max-w-3xl mx-auto mb-16 space-y-4">
      <h2
        class="text-3xl lg:text-4xl font-extrabold text-slate-900 tracking-tight"
      >
        来自全球用户的信任
      </h2>
      <p class="text-slate-500 text-lg leading-relaxed">
        成千上万的设计师、摄影师和电商卖家正在使用 QuickCut 提升他们的工作效率。
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
      <!-- 评价 1 -->
      <div
        class="bg-white p-8 rounded-[32px] border border-slate-100 shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition-shadow"
      >
        <div class="flex items-center space-x-1 text-orange-400 mb-6 text-sm">
          <i class="fas fa-star"></i><i class="fas fa-star"></i><i
            class="fas fa-star"></i><i class="fas fa-star"></i><i
            class="fas fa-star"></i>
        </div>
        <p class="text-slate-600 italic leading-relaxed mb-8">
          “作为一名电商摄影师，我每天需要处理数百张产品图。QuickCut
          的抠图质量让我感到惊讶，尤其是边缘的柔和处理，省去了我大量的修图时间。”
        </p>
        <div class="flex items-center space-x-4">
          <div
            class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-indigo-100 flex items-center justify-center overflow-hidden"
          >
            <img
              src="https://i.pravatar.cc/150?u=1"
              alt="用户"
              class="w-full h-full object-cover"
            />
          </div>
          <div>
            <h4 class="font-bold text-slate-900">张小凡</h4>
            <p
              class="text-xs text-slate-400 font-medium uppercase tracking-wider"
            >
              独立摄影师
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- 评价 2 -->
      <div
        class="bg-white p-8 rounded-[32px] border border-slate-100 shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition-shadow"
      >
        <div class="flex items-center space-x-1 text-orange-400 mb-6 text-sm">
          <i class="fas fa-star"></i><i class="fas fa-star"></i><i
            class="fas fa-star"></i><i class="fas fa-star"></i><i
            class="fas fa-star"></i>
        </div>
        <p class="text-slate-600 italic leading-relaxed mb-8">
          “我试过很多去背景工具，但这个 AI
          引擎识别非常准确。即使是背景非常复杂的场景，它也能精准地把我的猫咪从杂乱的客厅里分离出来。”
        </p>
        <div class="flex items-center space-x-4">
          <div
            class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-purple-100 flex items-center justify-center overflow-hidden"
          >
            <img
              src="https://i.pravatar.cc/150?u=2"
              alt="用户"
              class="w-full h-full object-cover"
            />
          </div>
          <div>
            <h4 class="font-bold text-slate-900">Linda Wang</h4>
            <p
              class="text-xs text-slate-400 font-medium uppercase tracking-wider"
            >
              自媒体博主
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- 评价 3 -->
      <div
        class="bg-white p-8 rounded-[32px] border border-slate-100 shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition-shadow"
      >
        <div class="flex items-center space-x-1 text-orange-400 mb-6 text-sm">
          <i class="fas fa-star"></i><i class="fas fa-star"></i><i
            class="fas fa-star"></i><i class="fas fa-star"></i><i
            class="fas fa-star"></i>
        </div>
        <p class="text-slate-600 italic leading-relaxed mb-8">
          “极其惊艳的响应速度！免费版居然能提供这么高质量的 HD
          图片下载，真的是良心产品。现在它已经是我浏览器收藏夹里的必备工具。”
        </p>
        <div class="flex items-center space-x-4">
          <div
            class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-blue-100 flex items-center justify-center overflow-hidden"
          >
            <img
              src="https://i.pravatar.cc/150?u=3"
              alt="用户"
              class="w-full h-full object-cover"
            />
          </div>
          <div>
            <h4 class="font-bold text-slate-900">李华</h4>
            <p
              class="text-xs text-slate-400 font-medium uppercase tracking-wider"
            >
              UI 设计师
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- 新增评价模块 -->
    <div class="mt-16 flex justify-center">
      <ReviewComponent client:visible />
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
